item.title: Time Travel, Love & the Great Fire with Kathy Forti
item.description: In this episode of Closer to Venus, host Johnny Burke interviews Dr. Kathy Forti, a clinical psychologist, Egyptian mystery school teacher, and author. They discuss her latest book, 'Portal to Passion,' which combines elements of time travel, romance, and the historic 1835 fire in New York. Dr. Forti explains her fascination with the fire, its impact on New York's development, and the historical opium trade's karmic consequences.
